      "title": "Security will be tightened around the Parliament",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Since the election of the President will be done tomorrow (20th), special security has been deployed around the Parliament from today (19th).",
        "It is also seen that army guards are deployed in the entrance ways of the Parliament and around the Parliament."
